{
  "id": "5c4e7231c1c1bd00171cb066",
  "title": "機能的固着の克服",
  "created": 1548644925,
  "updated": 1550321858,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5c4e7231c1c1bd00171cb066",
      "text": "機能的固着の克服",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548644925,
      "updated": 1548647838
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4e723daff09e0000c08d6a",
      "text": "[モチベーション3.0] p.89",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548644925,
      "updated": 1548647845
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680340aff09e00005be765",
      "text": "\tものの意外な別の使い方を見つけさせるテスト",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320449,
      "updated": 1550320463
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68034faff09e00005be767",
      "text": "\t問題解決にかかる時間が上位25%なら5ドル、1番なら20ドルがもらえる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320463,
      "updated": 1550320554
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6803aaaff09e00005be768",
      "text": "\tという報酬を提示された群とされない群で比較した",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320554,
      "updated": 1550320568
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680478aff09e00005be776",
      "text": "\t報酬を提示されない群は5〜10分だった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320760,
      "updated": 1550320784
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6803c0aff09e00005be76c",
      "text": "\t報酬を提示されたグループは提示されなかった群より3分半時間がかかった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320577,
      "updated": 1550320598
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6803d6aff09e00005be76d",
      "text": "\t\t直感に反して、報酬が成果を損ねる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320598,
      "updated": 1550320612
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680407aff09e00005be770",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320647,
      "updated": 1550320647
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680407aff09e00005be771",
      "text": "\tダニエル・ピンクの解釈",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320647,
      "updated": 1550320660
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680414aff09e00005be772",
      "text": "\t\t報酬は焦点を狭める性質がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320660,
      "updated": 1550320702
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68041caff09e00005be773",
      "text": "\t\t解決への道筋がはっきりしているなら、注意を逸らさない効果がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320668,
      "updated": 1550320682
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68042aaff09e00005be774",
      "text": "\t\tしかし広い視野で考えることが必要なタスクには逆効果である",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320682,
      "updated": 1550320710
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6803b8aff09e00005be76b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320568,
      "updated": 1550320568
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680501aff09e00005be777",
      "text": "残念ながら実験論文が明確に引用されてない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320898,
      "updated": 1550320908
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680517aff09e00005be77b",
      "text": "テスト自体は1940年代にカール・ドウンカーが考えたもので",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320920,
      "updated": 1550320934
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68050baff09e00005be779",
      "text": "報酬の有無で時間を比較したのはサム・グラックスバーグらしい。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320908,
      "updated": 1550320950
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68050caff09e00005be77a",
      "text": "→[ロウソク問題 - Wikipedia https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E3%83%AD%E3%82%A6%E3%82%BD%E3%82%AF%E5%95%8F%E9%A1%8C] あった",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320909,
      "updated": 1550321165
    },
    {
      "id": "5c680501aff09e00005be778",
      "text": "\tGlucksberg, S., 1962. The influence of strength of drive on functional fixedness and perceptual recognition. Journal of experimental psychology, 63(1), p.36.",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320898,
      "updated": 1550321857
    },
    {
      "id": "5c6808c1aff09e00005be77c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550321857,
      "updated": 1550321858
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4e7240aff09e0000c08d6c",
      "text": "[ロウソクの実験]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548644928,
      "updated": 1550320447
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4e7f0faff09e0000318e87",
      "text": "[インセンティブ]が[機能的固着]の克服に逆効果",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548648207,
      "updated": 1548648231
    },
    {
      "id": "5c4e7f26aff09e0000318e88",
      "text": "インセンティブは[視野を狭める] #遮眼帯",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1548648231,
      "updated": 1548648258
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68033baff09e00005be762",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320444,
      "updated": 1550320444
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68033baff09e00005be763",
      "text": "[固定概念] [思い込み] [思い込みによる枠] [思考の枠] [既存の枠組み]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320444,
      "updated": 1550320444
    },
    {
      "id": "5c68033caff09e00005be764",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1550320444,
      "updated": 1550320721
    }
  ]
}